<div class="game_area_description" id="game_area_description">
 <h2>
  About This Game
 </h2>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
  Islantiles is a cozy roguelike deckbuilder where players craft, combine and strategize their way to success! Starting with a single island, you’ll gradually expand your settlement into a thriving town. As you settle a chain of beautiful islands, you’ll unlock, swap, and combine powerful technologies that reshape your entire strategy. How far can you go?
 </p>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
  <span class="bb_img_ctn">
   <video autoplay="" class="bb_img" crossorigin="anonymous" height="326" loop="" muted="" playsinline="" poster="https://shared.fastly.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3634010/extras/181dfd51ea1e4b763e09aefcbc307c2e.poster.avif?t=1777908668" width="780">
    <source src="https://shared.fastly.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3634010/extras/181dfd51ea1e4b763e09aefcbc307c2e.webm?t=1777908668" type="video/webm; codecs=vp9"/>
   </video>
  </span>
 </p>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
  Place buildings, gather resources, shape your deck and trigger satisfying card combos. Technologies don’t just improve your deck – they twist the core rules, changing how tiles interact, how you score and what kind of strategies you can build. Buy new technologies or sell old ones to adapt to special challenges and pivot your strategy.
 </p>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
  <span class="bb_img_ctn">
   <video autoplay="" class="bb_img" crossorigin="anonymous" height="326" loop="" muted="" playsinline="" poster="https://shared.fastly.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3634010/extras/27325e5c678e8d5ee585f6f48497af02.poster.avif?t=1777908668" width="780">
    <source src="https://shared.fastly.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3634010/extras/27325e5c678e8d5ee585f6f48497af02.webm?t=1777908668" type="video/webm; codecs=vp9"/>
   </video>
  </span>
 </p>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
  Every island is unique, and no two runs are the same. Master the art of cozy efficiency and grow your settlements to glory!
 </p>
 <h2 class="bb_tag">
  Islantiles offers:
 </h2>
 <ul class="bb_ul">
  <li>
   <p class="bb_paragraph">
    A unique blend of city puzzler and deck builder
   </p>
  </li>
  <li>
   <p class="bb_paragraph">
    Cozy but compelling roguelike gameplay
   </p>
  </li>
  <li>
   <p class="bb_paragraph">
    Develop and refine different strategies
   </p>
  </li>
  <li>
   <p class="bb_paragraph">
    Six different difficulty settings
   </p>
  </li>
  <li>
   <p class="bb_paragraph">
    100 hand-crafted islands to develop
   </p>
  </li>
  <li>
   <p class="bb_paragraph">
    More than 100 technologies, each with unique rules
   </p>
  </li>
  <li>
   <p class="bb_paragraph">
    Highscores & Leaderboards
   </p>
  </li>
  <li>
   <p class="bb_paragraph">
    Roguelite progression: no two runs are the same
   </p>
  </li>
 </ul>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
  <span class="bb_img_ctn">
   <video autoplay="" class="bb_img" crossorigin="anonymous" height="326" loop="" muted="" playsinline="" poster="https://shared.fastly.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3634010/extras/505e0ea2b13035d674d0a828096ff74d.poster.avif?t=1777908668" width="780">
